      <scopecontent id="aspace_d816fd31a871d095f45927b2e6218cf3">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This collection comprises a diary with original bindings and transcripts along with several etchings and other writings by John Reynolds.</p>
      </scopecontent>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_d81e6a7d976abb6343a3d6fd679bcd00">
